{"tid":721777,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(墨西哥) 左派特朗普: 應該特赦毒販","createTime":"2018-06-29T02:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T05:13:10.000Z","uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"77ece799baf1d1a4582dad05cb819301a1184c79","tid":721777,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:32:29.000Z","msg":"01稱條友做左派特朗普<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : &quot;例如兩人都屬民粹主義領袖，特朗普提出美國優先，奧布拉多爾也是主張墨西哥優先；特朗普奉行貿易保護主義，奧布拉多爾也一樣，奧夫布多爾競選時表示，在他的任期內，墨西哥人會使用當地出產的汽油、當地製造的食物，而不是從外國進口。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sinchew.com.my/node/1769140\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sinchew.com.my%2Fnode%2F1769140&d=IhhpZRtuF5vgy5gBgPYU3MP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=88c5ddfc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sinchew.com.my/node/1769140</a><br />\n<br />\n對近年猖獗的貪腐問題及暴力感到極度無力，墨西哥人將在星期日的大選中用選票懲罰現任執政黨，根據最新民調顯示，左翼總統候選人奧布拉多爾已大幅領先對手20%。<br />\n<br />\n根據墨西哥民調機構Parametria，奧布拉多爾支持度為45%；相較下，最接近的競爭對手安納亞的支持度為26.1%。反建制的奧布拉多爾，在民粹勢力於全球盛行之際，預料無意外將能大勝。<br />\n<br />\n他提出，<strong>以軍人對抗毒販&ldquo;以暴易暴&rdquo;的做法不可行，反而建議特赦毒販，以取得長久和平</strong>。但他這種&ldquo;大愛&rdquo;主張未必能取得20%游離選民的支持。"},{"pid":"b06cd85899572f9be6783f87cdc01c75f09cb782","tid":721777,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:33:15.000Z","msg":"自01:<br />\n<br />\n這一波謀殺、綁架以及其他與犯罪組織有關的暴力事件，始於上屆2006至2012年政府。<strong>當時卡爾德龍（Felipe Calderon）政府鐵腕打擊販毒集團，展開「毒品戰爭」，卻觸發更多暴力犯罪事件。不少不法分子更加滲透執法部門及地方政府</strong>，以至現屆的涅托（Enrique Pena Nieto）政府亦束手無策。"},{"pid":"3693bb21e251f10964b63d158c91e6bd1647c662","tid":721777,"uid":87780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:34:08.000Z","msg":"不如販毒合法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4f7cb8f4212378533a9632735f54169455c5ce","tid":721777,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3693bb21e251f10964b63d158c91e6bd1647c662","tid":721777,"uid":87780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:34:08.000Z","msg":"不如販毒合法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:37:28.000Z","msg":"條友似乎準備咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba58aecce64c4220df50f7a42c862e82b0cafc40","tid":721777,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T02:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7fc70344d8449088f8cd6b688ec7c7611b56e3","tid":721777,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04319bc484cdfeb5ae9d854156ede1fd64dedce5","tid":721777,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:40:29.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be7f90411ed2a826428b1b923ea14ca6d84f9fe","tid":721777,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:41:52.000Z","msg":"既然剷除唔到，就全部合法化，拉低市價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1c68cf362126d0683228c1af0eb46bba5e447e","tid":721777,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T05:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}